data.description: This is a once in a lifetime opportunity to own this Historic Landmark Designation Craftsman home in Grapevine’s Historic District just a few blocks from Main Street.  Historic Main Street is the location of amazing restaurants, beautiful wineries, and plenty of shopping.  Located on the corner of S Dooley and E Franklin with 0.37 acres, this home is ready for renovation.  With the home located in a Historic District and landmarked, you will need approval from the Preservation Commission prior to renovation and construction.  Please note this property is sold as is.
